"},{"range":"241","text":"242"},{"alt":"223"},{"range":"243","text":"244"},{"alt":"226"},{"range":"245","text":"246"},{"alt":"229"},{"range":"247","text":"248"},{"alt":"232"},{"range":"249","text":"250"},{"alt":"223"},{"range":"251","text":"252"},{"alt":"226"},{"range":"253","text":"254"},{"alt":"229"},{"range":"255","text":"256"},{"alt":"232"},{"range":"257","text":"258"},{"alt":"223"},{"range":"259","text":"260"},{"alt":"226"},{"range":"261","text":"262"},{"alt":"229"},{"range":"263","text":"264"},{"alt":"232"},{"range":"265","text":"266"},{"alt":"223"},{"range":"267","text":"268"},{"alt":"226"},{"range":"269","text":"270"},{"alt":"229"},{"range":"271","text":"272"},{"alt":"232"},{"range":"273","text":"274"},{"alt":"223"},{"range":"275","text":"276"},{"alt":"226"},{"range":"277","text":"278"},{"alt":"229"},{"range":"279","text":"280"},{"alt":"232"},{"range":"281","text":"282"},"&apos;",[544,689],"\n          A selection of machine learning models, NLP pipelines, and AI systems I&apos;ve built, including several implemented from scratch.\n        ","&lsquo;",[544,689],"\n          A selection of machine learning models, NLP pipelines, and AI systems I&lsquo;ve built, including several implemented from scratch.\n        ","&#39;",[544,689],"\n          A selection of machine learning models, NLP pipelines, and AI systems I&#39;ve built, including several implemented from scratch.\n        ","&rsquo;",[544,689],"\n          A selection of machine learning models, NLP pipelines, and AI systems I&rsquo;ve built, including several implemented from scratch.\n        ",[4098,4510],"\n          These implementations are part of rigorous coursework at ENSA Safi&apos;s engineering program in Computer Science and AI. Rather than relying on pre-built libraries, each project emphasizes understanding the mathematical foundations and algorithmic design of modern AI systems. This approach builds deep expertise in neural networks, natural language processing, and machine learning fundamentals.\n        ",[4098,4510],"\n          These implementations are part of rigorous coursework at ENSA Safi&lsquo;s engineering program in Computer Science and AI. Rather than relying on pre-built libraries, each project emphasizes understanding the mathematical foundations and algorithmic design of modern AI systems. This approach builds deep expertise in neural networks, natural language processing, and machine learning fundamentals.\n        ",[4098,4510],"\n          These implementations are part of rigorous coursework at ENSA Safi&#39;s engineering program in Computer Science and AI. Rather than relying on pre-built libraries, each project emphasizes understanding the mathematical foundations and algorithmic design of modern AI systems. This approach builds deep expertise in neural networks, natural language processing, and machine learning fundamentals.\n        ",[4098,4510],"\n          These implementations are part of rigorous coursework at ENSA Safi&rsquo;s engineering program in Computer Science and AI. Rather than relying on pre-built libraries, each project emphasizes understanding the mathematical foundations and algorithmic design of modern AI systems. This approach builds deep expertise in neural networks, natural language processing, and machine learning fundamentals.\n        ",[549,671],"\n          A selection of full-stack web applications and SaaS products I&apos;ve built using modern web technologies.\n        ",[549,671],"\n          A selection of full-stack web applications and SaaS products I&lsquo;ve built using modern web technologies.\n        ",[549,671],"\n          A selection of full-stack web applications and SaaS products I&#39;ve built using modern web technologies.\n        ",[549,671],"\n          A selection of full-stack web applications and SaaS products I&rsquo;ve built using modern web technologies.\n        ",[800,1018],"\n            I&apos;m Mouaad Essaghir, a first-year engineering student at ENSA Safi (École Nationale des Sciences Appliquées, Université Cadi Ayyad), specializing in Computer Science and Artificial Intelligence.\n          ",[800,1018],"\n            I&lsquo;m Mouaad Essaghir, a first-year engineering student at ENSA Safi (École Nationale des Sciences Appliquées, Université Cadi Ayyad), specializing in Computer Science and Artificial Intelligence.\n          ",[800,1018],"\n            I&#39;m Mouaad Essaghir, a first-year engineering student at ENSA Safi (École Nationale des Sciences Appliquées, Université Cadi Ayyad), specializing in Computer Science and Artificial Intelligence.\n          ",[800,1018],"\n            I&rsquo;m Mouaad Essaghir, a first-year engineering student at ENSA Safi (École Nationale des Sciences Appliquées, Université Cadi Ayyad), specializing in Computer Science and Artificial Intelligence.\n          ",[1120,1374],"\n            I&apos;m passionate about AI, LLMs, and generative AI — and I build things from scratch to truly understand them. Currently working on a large-scale SaaS product that brings together AI, web, desktop, and mobile into a single platform.\n          ",[1120,1374],"\n            I&lsquo;m passionate about AI, LLMs, and generative AI — and I build things from scratch to truly understand them. Currently working on a large-scale SaaS product that brings together AI, web, desktop, and mobile into a single platform.\n          ",[1120,1374],"\n            I&#39;m passionate about AI, LLMs, and generative AI — and I build things from scratch to truly understand them. Currently working on a large-scale SaaS product that brings together AI, web, desktop, and mobile into a single platform.\n          ",[1120,1374],"\n            I&rsquo;m passionate about AI, LLMs, and generative AI — and I build things from scratch to truly understand them. Currently working on a large-scale SaaS product that brings together AI, web, desktop, and mobile into a single platform.\n          ",[1471,1571],"\n            I&apos;m looking for new challenges to grow my technical and professional skills.\n          ",[1471,1571],"\n            I&lsquo;m looking for new challenges to grow my technical and professional skills.\n          ",[1471,1571],"\n            I&#39;m looking for new challenges to grow my technical and professional skills.\n          ",[1471,1571],"\n            I&rsquo;m looking for new challenges to grow my technical and professional skills.\n          ",[2228,2298],"\n              ✓ Message sent! I&apos;ll get back to you soon.\n            ",[2228,2298],"\n              ✓ Message sent! I&lsquo;ll get back to you soon.\n            ",[2228,2298],"\n              ✓ Message sent! I&#39;ll get back to you soon.\n            ",[2228,2298],"\n              ✓ Message sent! I&rsquo;ll get back to you soon.\n            "]